reviewText: Have been a big fan of the Jiburiru series!!!  I recommend this series for any hentai lovers!!! The only negative is that this series isn't english dubbed!!!

this movie is still in the first series so its not the 3rd series at all(the first series had 4 eps this is the third if your wondering). also this is censored if your wondering as well there are uncensored ones out there if u look hard enough. either way the series is still good
